#: ../../whatsnew/2.7.rst:262
msgid ""
"Comparing two ordered dictionaries checks both the keys and values, and "
"requires that the insertion order was the same::"
msgstr "比较两个有序字典会同时检查键和值，并要求插入顺序相同 ::"

